data.description: Located in a quiet cul-de-sac in the esteemed Park Hill neighborhood of Derby, this beautiful 5BR, 3Bth home features a formal dining room, beautiful gas fireplace, split bedroom floor plan with a convenient mid-level walkout basement.  The large primary suite has a walk-in closet, double sinks, separate soaker tub and shower, and a private walk out to the deck.  The basement features 2 additional bedrooms, spacious family room with custom built in entertainment center, custom wet bar with pull out shelves, and a wall fridge to keep beverages cold.  The fully fenced backyard makes entertaining fun and easy with a partially covered deck, a large concrete patio, and best of all, no backyard neighbors!  The sellers loved the close access to the elementary school which made it possible for their child to walk to and from school while being observed from the back deck or for easy pickup on rainy days.  The home has an irrigation well with a new pump and a new roof with a transferable 5-year warranty that was put on in May 2023.  The neighborhood features a pond and swimming pool.  Conveniently located close to McConnell Air Force Base, shopping, and dining this home is waiting for your family!  Assumable loan under 3%!  Don’t let this one pass you by, schedule your private showing today.
